Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.14,0:02:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Natsume, Ishimura.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.29,0:02:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, once the exam's over, the rest is easy.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.14,0:02:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go somewhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.99,0:02:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Fishing, maybe?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.57,0:02:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.72,0:02:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.92,0:02:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you want to go?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.87,0:02:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.30,0:02:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.58,0:02:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me in on that.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.00,0:02:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasada...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.40,0:02:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got something cool.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.33,0:02:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.13,0:02:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad's friend gave him these.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.34,0:02:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all go together.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.82,0:02:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,An art museum?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.71,0:02:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.80,0:02:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really far away.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.27,0:02:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on, the exam's over!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.19,0:02:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer's come again.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.45,0:03:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.42,0:03:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.35,0:03:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome back, Takashi.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.80,0:03:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this? It's from a class reunion.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.94,0:03:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,From elementary school.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.73,0:03:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yours?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.04,0:03:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking about those days.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.04,0:03:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm so old now!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.44,0:03:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess everyone else is, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.78,0:03:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I miss being a kid.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.95,0:03:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, there's something that's been bothering me a little.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.00,0:03:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you hear me out, Takashi?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.54,0:03:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.37,0:03:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Once, a bunch of us good friends exchanged presents.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.88,0:04:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody said that they would make something.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.26,0:04:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We were all so excited.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.09,0:04:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We all sang around in a circle,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.35,0:04:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and I ended up with Kuriyama's handmade cookies.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.30,0:04:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama got the pressed flower cards I made.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.48,0:04:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But... she looked so unhappy.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.89,0:04:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"I didn't want something like this!"
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.63,0:04:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"You're no fair, Touko!"
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.94,0:04:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"Give me back my cookies!"
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.28,0:04:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.39,0:04:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've apologized.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.92,0:04:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think she or anybody else remembers it, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.67,0:04:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.72,0:04:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama moved away, after that.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.33,0:04:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to see her again.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.81,0:04:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I want to talk about what happened.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.66,0:04:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I just think that if I saw that she was doing well,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.59,0:05:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,this thing that's been bothering me would just vanish.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.99,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,I was a bit jealous.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.99,0:05:13.20,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,I don't have any good memories of my childhood.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.29,0:05:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.17,0:05:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so great about going to an art museum?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.59,0:05:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody asked you to come.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.87,0:05:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I think Sasada said there was a good ramen place nearby.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.77,0:05:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramen?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.91,0:05:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ramen? Ramen? Ramen?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.94,0:05:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sneak into my bag again.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.40,0:05:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.88,0:05:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You just said you weren't!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.19,0:05:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going, I'm going, I'm going!{said four times?}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.44,0:05:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not taking you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.37,0:05:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ra... ramen...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.83,0:05:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.47,0:05:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay here and watch the house!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.99,0:05:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.60,0:05:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.12,0:05:59.21,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Now my days are full of fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.53,0:05:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramen!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.45,0:05:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going!{unsubbed line after}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.51,0:06:07.19,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's quiet.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.24,0:06:11.17,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Summer's here.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.17,0:06:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hold my breath for ten minutes!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.48,0:06:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's useless!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.98,0:06:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not useless!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.85,0:06:19.57,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I guess it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.57,0:06:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I heard you found something cool?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.65,0:06:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I found a big bug.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.90,0:06:35.37,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Being invisible is honestly really useless.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.37,0:06:38.68,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Humans just walk past me.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.34,0:06:41.34,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like the seasons.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.34,0:06:47.13,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was that summer, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.66,0:06:51.85,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There was one person...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.09,0:06:54.60,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}who could see me.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really pretty.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.13,0:07:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.79,0:07:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.44,0:07:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you'll get in trouble.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.53,0:07:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.84,0:07:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's watching.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do with that branch?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.75,0:07:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Just toss it.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.73,0:07:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You suck.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.54,0:07:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How arrogant! How rude!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.04,0:07:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Those insensitive lower organisms
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.59,0:07:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,can't even sense a noble being like me!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.68,0:07:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Nose hair!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.77,0:07:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What a crappy day.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.75,0:07:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be something that could cheer me up.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.94,0:07:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, the liar's coming.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.13,0:07:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, the liar's here!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.86,0:07:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get close to him, you'll turn into a liar too!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.55,0:07:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You totally will!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.91,0:07:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.99,0:07:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoo-shoo!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.87,0:07:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mocking their companions at such a young age.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.99,0:07:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How ugly.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.79,0:07:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.29,0:08:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.63,0:08:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.96,0:08:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that rock came from the sky.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.81,0:08:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the kind of lie you'd tell, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.02,0:08:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.84,0:08:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Noisy brats.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.01,0:08:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.50,0:08:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, say something!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.81,0:08:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.30,0:08:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Bugs!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.06,0:08:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That was wonderful!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.05,0:08:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I think... he looked right at me...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.15,0:08:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.10,0:08:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody can see me.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.33,0:08:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans can't see spirits.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.34,0:08:52.64,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nobody can see me.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.02,0:09:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You really can—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.07,0:09:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a rude kid!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.15,0:09:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't forget this!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.11,0:09:17.04,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For every day after that, I chased him,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.53,0:09:19.54,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}lied in ambush,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.12,0:09:22.73,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and scared him.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.50,0:09:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.49,0:09:25.84,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He always ran away.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.54,0:09:29.47,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was all, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.51,0:09:34.34,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it was kind of fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.43,0:09:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, where is he today?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.18,0:09:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, he transferred, didn't he?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.44,0:09:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I heard he's creepy.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.91,0:09:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He tells weird lies.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.28,0:09:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Lies?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.45,0:09:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He says he can see monsters just to get attention.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.32,0:09:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard he doesn't have any parents and nobody wants him,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.87,0:09:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,so he keeps transferring.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.56,0:10:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he's always alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.18,0:10:03.84,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's always alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.06,0:10:08.75,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just because he can see us.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.34,0:10:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.49,0:10:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.17,0:10:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I made an elephant today!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.03,0:10:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.93,0:10:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And I did a handstand!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.61,0:10:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You got scared! You were scared, weren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.23,0:10:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.03,0:10:36.45,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the first time he's spoken to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.87,0:10:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you care about me?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.70,0:10:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you bored?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.86,0:10:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Bored?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.96,0:10:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.08,0:10:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't be stupid!{added stutter}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.67,0:10:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I just happened to be passing by.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.26,0:10:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody as important as me has lots of stuff to do!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.55,0:10:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about somebody like you.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.69,0:10:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.05,0:10:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.48,0:11:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with him?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.95,0:11:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.32,0:11:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nose hair!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.65,0:11:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Look at that! It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.29,0:11:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah, it's beautiful!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.28,0:11:58.16,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used to live around here.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.16,0:11:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Shut up about the ramen.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.24,0:12:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Natsume? You're spacing out.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.41,0:12:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What, are you hungry, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.62,0:12:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.48,0:12:13.79,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My relatives passed me from one house to another.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.79,0:12:17.34,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I don't remember exactly where I was.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.34,0:12:18.46,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.16,0:12:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.98,0:12:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one with the problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.93,0:12:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I need you to take him next week.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.48,0:12:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the deal!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.35,0:12:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.92,0:12:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're back.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.53,0:12:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... you, well... well...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.04,0:12:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be living at my brother's house starting next week.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.07,0:12:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My kid's got college exams this year.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.95,0:12:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And... oh, right.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.23,0:13:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you this coat.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.57,0:13:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be a bit big, but that's no problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.04,0:13:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.05,0:13:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think badly of me.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.53,0:13:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,For, well, everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.92,0:13:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of dusty.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.20,0:13:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And just when we'd finally spoken.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.25,0:13:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to say that.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.53,0:13:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.48,0:13:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to be nice to some human kid?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.14,0:13:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, I'll scare him like always.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.31,0:13:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.56,0:13:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If I scare him, he might talk to me again.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.04,0:14:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd you get that coat?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.18,0:14:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}He's here!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.04,0:14:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My uncle gave it to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.54,0:14:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.83,0:14:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}All right, now!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.49,0:14:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.93,0:14:24.66,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,Oww...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.66,0:14:25.93,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.93,0:14:28.13,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,I'm soaked!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.13,0:14:29.93,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,What was that for?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.47,0:14:33.44,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shoot! I didn't mean to do that.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.44,0:14:34.52,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.52,0:14:35.67,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,I just...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.67,0:14:36.81,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,Get lost.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.37,0:14:39.87,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.89,0:14:42.99,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,What did I do to you?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.56,0:14:46.20,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,Why do I...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.28,0:14:51.19,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,I hate you all!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.88,0:15:01.42,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was last day he took this path.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.20,0:15:06.97,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It felt like he was taking the long way around to school.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.83,0:15:14.48,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't think he'll listen to me anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.31,0:15:17.81,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He won't see me anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.30,0:15:22.57,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.59,0:15:49.29,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,He's alone again.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.95,0:15:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a kitty.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.82,0:16:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.95,0:16:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You smell kind of nice.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.95,0:16:21.84,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He looks so kind...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.05,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's warm.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.05,0:16:33.39,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to stay by him forever.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.53,0:16:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be nice to be you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.09,0:16:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be alone, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.31,0:16:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to live by myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.09,0:16:58.61,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm a spirit, so I don't understand humans.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.16,0:17:04.05,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's sad to be alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.05,0:17:06.29,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know that.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.29,0:17:08.29,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If nothing else, I know that.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.21,0:17:16.85,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A few days ago, he was taken far away.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.77,0:17:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.60,0:17:21.28,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who's that woman?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.28,0:17:23.61,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her lips and nails are bright red.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.61,0:17:26.74,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that man's eyes keep shifting around.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.11,0:17:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take him.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.01,0:17:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a kid your age.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.24,0:17:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it. You'll get used to it soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.82,0:17:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Mommy?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.69,0:17:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.45,0:17:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We're a fun family.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.33,0:17:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After that...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.34,0:17:53.20,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never saw him again.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.59,0:17:58.10,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So what if I'm alone?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.35,0:18:01.43,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's much better to be alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.17,0:18:06.85,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why do those humans always want to be with each other?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.56,0:18:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What pretty flowers!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.29,0:18:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.01,0:18:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.54,0:18:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.43,0:18:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. Something touched my hand.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.71,0:18:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. That's scary!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.92,0:18:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough of this.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.55,0:18:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.88,0:18:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how long am I supposed to take care of your mother?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.13,0:18:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't say that.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.61,0:18:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.64,0:18:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of this.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.06,0:18:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sick of this? {You can't...}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.89,0:18:44.48,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What an ugly, twisted face.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.14,0:18:50.48,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I really hate humans.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.48,0:18:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just take care of her?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.37,0:18:56.28,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish they'd all just disappear.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.12,0:19:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate them!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.16,0:19:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate them all!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.66,0:19:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Those ugly things that only think about themselves...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.39,0:19:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish they'd all disappear!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.13,0:19:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it's dangerous to go under that tree.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.76,0:19:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know everything,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.05,0:19:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but something scary's supposed to happen.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.57,0:19:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.56,0:19:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.00,0:19:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.41,0:19:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.58,0:19:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A cat!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.37,0:19:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate cats!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.62,0:19:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.77,0:19:54.66,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't think anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.66,0:19:56.20,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't think at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.42,0:19:59.72,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Time has stopped for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.51,0:20:03.43,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's he doing now?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.60,0:20:07.19,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With his kind smile, and his sad wish...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.48,0:20:11.54,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is he smiling?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.90,0:20:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.51,0:20:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still here.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.67,0:20:29.29,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know how many seasons it's been,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.83,0:20:31.98,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I've never forgotten.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.59,0:20:35.34,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've always remembered.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.71,0:20:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It was bothering me.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.61,0:20:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We said goodbye in such a strange way.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.15,0:20:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.63,0:20:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, I could only get mad at others,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.47,0:20:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,but now, I think I understand your kindness.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.81,0:20:56.79,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure he's met another kind soul...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.79,0:20:58.78,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}if he can smile like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.52,0:21:08.54,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I remember this smell.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.62,0:21:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Natsume Takashi.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.25,0:21:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you tell me your name?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.62,0:21:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.06,0:21:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.72,0:21:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.26,0:21:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.44,0:21:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You met her, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.84,0:21:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what about you?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.69,0:21:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have fun?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.23,0:21:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.03,0:21:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.94,0:21:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I had one, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.82,0:21:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You want to make a stop somewhere?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.70,0:21:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, there's somebody I want to find.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.54,0:21:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an old friend,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.93,0:21:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't know if I can see them.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.33,0:21:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Go have fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.57,0:21:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just head home.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.00,0:21:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.83,0:21:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.92,0:22:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.84,0:22:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.78,0:22:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.16,0:22:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good time!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.93,0:22:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.86,0:22:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.15,0:22:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I understand now.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:21.44,0:22:24.01,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If there's somebody you want to see,
